    "assessments.",
    "This embedding model provides the feature vectors of the generated report and the ground truth, allowing us to compute their cosine similarity as a measure of semantic understanding.",
    "To go beyond the domain-specific use of language, we apply a general large-scale embedding model, GPT-3-ADA 26, to capture a broader range of linguistic information.",
    "Similarly, we use BERTScore 55 to compute the syntactic relationship between generated and ground truth reports at the subword level.",
    "For ensemble refinement, we summarize the bootstrapped reports by prompting GPT-4-Turbo with the instruction \"Summarize the following text:\"."
  ],
